quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  23,91,"Allah nganalitendela mwanache jwalijose, soni pangali nnungu jwine pamo ni Jwalakwe, ingaŵe iyyo (kuti paliji pana nnungujwine) nikuti nnungu jwalijose jungajigalaga yajugumbile (ni kwakanya achimilungu ŵane kuituma), soni ŵane mwa ŵanganyao angalinjilile kuŵa pachanya pa ŵane (pakanganilana umwenye). Allah aŵambalene nayo kusyene yaakusimba ŵanganyao."
  23,92,"Nkumanyilila yakusisika ni yakuonechela, basi Jwalakwe jutukwiche kwannope ku yaakum’bwanganya nayoyo."
  23,93,"Jilani (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ): “Ambuje ŵangu! Naga timunosye (ilagasyo) yaakuŵa nkupedwa chilanga ŵanganyao,”"
  25,37,"Nombe nao ŵandu ŵa Nuhu; ndema jaŵaakaaniile achimitenga, twamisisye (ni chigumula), ni twatesile kuŵa chilosyo kwa ŵandu. Sano ŵalupuso twalinganyichisye ilagasyo yakupoteka nnope."
  25,38,"Nambo soni achina Adi, achina Samuda, achimisyene chisima kwisa soni mikutula jejinji ja chilikati chao."
  25,39,"Soni jwalijose (mwa ŵanganyao), twampele ilandanyo (kuŵa maumboni ni ijiiganyo), soni ŵaliose (mwa ŵanganyao) twajonasile kusyene (panyuma pakwakanila achimitenga ŵao)."
  26,10,"Soni (kumbuchilani) katema kaŵam’bilasile Ambuje ŵenu Musa (ni kuntenda kuti): “Jaulani ku ŵandu ŵalupuso.”"
  26,11,"“Ŵandu ŵa Firiauna; ana ngakogopa?”"
  26,12,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Ambuje ŵangu! Chisimu une ngogopa kuti chakanganile.”"